# APM dependencies

When editing `home/dot_apm/apm.yml`, keep the `dependencies.apm` entries sorted.

- Sort every entry under `dependencies: apm:` after changing that list.
- Compare entries by the full dependency string exactly as written.
- Preserve the existing YAML structure and quoting style.
